    "Name": "Spatha",
    "Details": "While its body is the height of high tech, for the most part the Spathas weaponry is relatively common for the era. The Spathas main weapon is the Sword it is named after, deadly enough before the triple strength myomer kicks in. Its ranged weaponry consists of an ER PPC with a PPC Capacitor, and two Medium X-Pulse Lasers and a Streak SRM-6 launcher for shorter ranges.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Reinforced Legs</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>",
